@prefix bao:  <https://w3id.org/boolean-algebra-ontology#>.
@prefix rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>.
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>.
@prefix sh:   <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#>.
@prefix :   <http://www.example.org#>.


# The first triple below asserts that Bill is married to Mary, while the second triple asserts that this fact is false.
# Therefore, a contradiction is inferred in the knowledge graph.

:Bill :hasWife :Mary.
<<:Bill :hasWife :Mary>> rdf:type bao:False.

